Global Aramid Powder Market Insights
Aramid Powder Market size was valued at USD 1.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.5 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 10.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Aramid Powder Market Overview
The global Aramid Powder Market is experiencing significant growth due to the increasing demand for aramid fibers across various industries, including automotive, aerospace, and electronics. The market value was estimated at approximately USD 1.7 billion in 2024, and it is expected to grow at a robust CAGR of 5.6% over the forecast period. This growth is primarily driven by the increasing application of aramid powder in advanced composite materials, which are widely used for their lightweight, durable, and heat-resistant properties. The market is also benefiting from the rising focus on sustainability and the growing use of aramid-based products in industrial applications. The growing industrial sector and advancements in technology further contribute to the market expansion.

